{"tid":333401,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好鍾意醉醉地但又醉唔哂嗰種感覺","createTime":"2017-07-23T18:39:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T20:58:39.000Z","uid":10214,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1d4cfc577045fc7e02e1679bb7573a1852bc05a3","tid":333401,"uid":10214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:39:21.000Z","msg":"大約十年前第一次接觸酒精已經愛上了<br />\n嗰陣幾個中學雞柴娃娃吹下水聽下歌咁又一晚<br />\n直到人愈大<br />\n朋友各有各忙<br />\n彼此愈嚟愈少聯絡<br />\n就算聯絡返發現大家對事物嘅睇法或價值觀已經南轅北轍<br />\n此時<br />\n已冇必要去聯絡了<br />\n不經不覺<br />\n已經習慣了自己一個飲酒 自己一個作樂<br />\n自己說自己 <br />\n下雨天也自己笑<br />\n反而成為一種樂趣<br />\n有幸遇上一位知己<br />\n酒逢知己千杯少<br />\n話不投機半句多<br />\n這個道理又有誰能參透<br />\n<br />\n脷伸：飲緊<br />\n千杯不碎"},{"pid":"d256aca3c28637279f0304fade5e2a4e04c00805","tid":333401,"uid":10214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:41:31.000Z","msg":"更正：自己說自己<span style=\"color: red;\">笑</span>"},{"pid":"7b3f257c8c2f738cc51a3f096f69336dc7452f6c","tid":333401,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:42:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f7043b32aabc87d273497cd68cc6f156270c59d","tid":333401,"uid":29118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:43:47.000Z","msg":"醉緊 想瞓又瞓唔到"},{"pid":"75a884b7febef0d80f735473194fde3ea6b95753","tid":333401,"uid":10214,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:51:21.000Z","msg":"酒精和尼古丁對身體有害眾所皆知<br />\n諷刺嘅係愈對身體有害嘅嘢愈能令人釋懷"},{"pid":"387372fce2ffe94e0a473b1da8880ceed4ada95b","tid":333401,"uid":1355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:53:03.000Z","msg":"好鐘意飲到行唔到正線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a533a105fa23e8be1fd6eb750a109b79ad8563ad","tid":333401,"uid":1355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T18:53:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好鐘意飲到行唔到<span style=\"color: red;\">直</span>線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></bloc